    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "If you love cars with personality, this one has it in spades. It\u2019s the kind of ride that turns an ordinary driveway into the start of a story\u2014full of charm, presence, and the sort of lived-in character enthusiasts often appreciate. A great fit for someone seeking an affordable entry point, a hands-on project, or a dependable extra set of wheels with unmistakable spirit. It\u2019s not pretending to be showroom fresh; instead, it offers opportunity, attitude, and a chance to make it your own.",
