    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next owner, this vehicle offers practical transportation at an approachable price point. It shows its age cosmetically and is best suited for a buyer seeking straightforward value, a starter vehicle, or a project with potential. If you want an inexpensive option with honest appeal and room to make it your own, this is a compelling opportunity.",
