      "description": "Honest little car that\u2019s best suited for someone after affordable wheels or a handy project. It\u2019s not winning any beauty contests, but it\u2019s a straightforward budget-friendly option with plenty of life left for the right buyer. If you want something cheap, practical, and sold by someone who\u2019ll tell it to you straight, this is well worth a look.",
